{"tid":592813,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"最聯淪落到比李城抽水串 李斯特城：去年今天我們贏了西維爾","createTime":"2018-03-14T13:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T17:43:58.000Z","uid":94771,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a93d4385cbbef5747a0bab8e642b1e664f48ea8e","tid":592813,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T13:35:32.000Z","msg":"香港時間3月14日淩晨，英超球隊曼聯在歐冠盃淘汰賽中1-2主場不敵西維爾，總比數1-2被淘汰。而在當天下午，英超球隊李斯特城官方Twitter發文：「去年的今天，我們2-0擊敗了西維爾。」這也引發了球迷們的熱議。<br />\n<br />\n　　在上季的歐冠盃16強中，英超冠軍李斯特城抽到了西班牙球隊西維爾，最終他們在首回合1-2不敵對手的情況下，次回合2-0擊敗對手逆轉晉級。摩根和阿爾白禮頓破門成為了球隊的功臣，其中小舒米高還撲出了一粒12碼。<br />\n<br />\n　　李斯特城的兩粒入球<br />\n<br />\n　　李斯特城的這條Twitter也引發了球迷的熱議，不少國外球迷認為這是在嘲諷曼聯，不知道大家怎麼看呢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8475c772b9b64f61947b5071684fbddc4a160f5b","tid":592813,"uid":94771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T13:37:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LCFC/status/973825054105587717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLCFC%2Fstatus%2F973825054105587717&d=PCXXq2x%2FEDCv2h6wDdiBy54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=0fbfea2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLCFC%2Fstatus%2F973825054105587717&h=bbc98b10\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LCFC/status/973825054105587717</a>"},{"pid":"ccd5f0732903f6c958bcf23c437c4721f4acf5c3","tid":592813,"uid":9231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T13:37:45.000Z","msg":"我曼有既係歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66a3aae8d00acb3cda5472880a48cdc96ca08ff","tid":592813,"uid":47496,"like":5,"